title: Van Morrison - 2016-01-18 - Oakland Ca US
description:
This is a very nice new Van Morrison recording.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Van Morrison
Fox Theater
Oakland, Ca
January 18,2015

Recorded by Daspyknows

Recorded Loge - Center  Row A  
  
Schoeps MK4/NBox Platinum Tascam DR-2D 24 Bit 48K 

Processed using Soundforge 11, resample, to 16bit 44.1K
TLH to convert to Flac

Master 2016.02


01. Celtic Swing
02. Close Enough for Jazz
03. I Believe to My Soul (Ray Charles cover)
04. Back on Top
05. Magic Time
06. By His Grace
07. Sometimes I Feel Like a Motherless Child (Paul Robeson cover)
08. Northern Muse (Solid Ground) (with guest organ player John Allair)
09. Satisfied (with guest organ player John Allair)
10. Days Like This
11. Brown Eyed Girl
12. Wild Night
13. Sometimes We Cry (with Shana Morrison)
14. That Old Black Magic (Johnny Mercer cover) (with Shana Morrison)
15. Carrying a Torch
16. Baby, Please Don't Go / Parchman Farm / Don't Start Crying Now
17. Whenever God Shines His Light
18. Moondance
19. Help Me (Sonny Boy Williamson cover)
20. Gloria / Who Do You Love
 

First show of 2016.  Tickets were at will call so I did not know where I was
sitting.  I arrived and picked up front row loge seats which is a great spot
to record.  Van Morrison put on a great performance and the recording does it
justice.  Great crowd except the asshats behind me who talked most of the show.  
Fortunately I could lean forward which meant I didn't need to listen to them.  
 

 

Just the basic taper requests here and please no vitriol:
Don't be an ass by selling this or using it in a video that is sold
Don't modify the info file
Don't remaster and/or post on other sites that are not 100% free 
If shared keep info file intact but create a second file with any changes
Don't convert to lossy formats except for personal use
Do support the artists
